This paper deals with data poisoning attacks on deep neural networks, which is a topic related to machine learning and computer security. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
